start in room 0
go north to room 1 and fight guy with your fists (knight maybe?)
	once you fight him, you get his sword.
then, go to room 2, and fight an undead knight with the newly acquired sword
go north to room3, talk to the blacksmith and get the sword upgrade for free
go to the east in room4 where you fight a magician
go south to room5 to get 5 gold pieces
go back to blacksmith to get your sword upgraded again
go back to room4, then north to room6 to fight shield guy, take his shield
go south, then east to room7 and use the shield to fight arrow man, take his key
go all the way west to room8 and use the key to open the door, fight the evil prince, take the crown
